00:13:37.533 --> 00:13:38.900
call them adaptive if you'd like.

00:13:38.900 --> 00:13:39.662
That's already built.

00:13:39.662 --> 00:13:41.338
Actually, I started building that before

00:13:41.338 --> 00:13:43.107
I started working on the videos.

00:13:43.107 --> 00:13:44.879
The videos are actually a
complement to the software piece,

00:13:44.879 --> 00:13:45.797
