00:13:50.274 --> 00:13:51.784
It's on an app engine.

00:13:52.599 --> 00:13:53.993
People started coming out of the woodwork,

00:13:53.993 --> 00:13:54.871
started working on that,

00:13:54.871 --> 00:13:56.876
so it's an open source
project on top of that,

00:13:56.877 --> 00:14:00.760
so not only will Khan
Academy be a virtual school,

00:14:00.760 --> 00:14:02.789
