00:14:49.944 --> 00:14:51.617
and then you and I will have
a session not too different

00:14:51.617 --> 00:14:54.136
than I was having with
my cousins 4 years ago,

00:14:54.136 --> 00:14:55.324
and then we'll also record it,

00:14:55.324 --> 00:14:57.033
so it also becomes part of this library

00:14:57.033 --> 00:14:58.658
that we can collect all
of this data around.

00:14:58.658 --> 00:14:59.933
Was that a good interaction?

00:14:59.933 --> 00:15:01.656
I'll rate you, you'll rate me,

00:15:01.656 --> 00:15:03.615
