people who are doing exercises,

00:15:18.322 --> 00:15:20.009
and there are other people
who are starting to explore

00:15:20.009 --> 00:15:21.566
the peer-to-peer learning,

00:15:21.566 --> 00:15:23.483
but I'm pretty convinced
in order to do it properly,

00:15:23.483 --> 00:15:27.584
you want to have all of them
together in the same place.

00:15:27.584 --> 00:15:31.282
Andrew: Okay, so we got the videos today.

